bin ikh tsugegangen, zi hot shoyn nisht gekent k- tun gornisht,

00:27:31.173 --> 00:27:33.198
hot zi mir gezotgt, Yankl, nem azoy.

00:27:33.198 --> 00:27:34.252
tu azoy.

00:27:34.252 --> 00:27:37.062
ikh hob dir nor derlangt esn, deys iz ⟨dir⟩ gefeln gevorn.

00:27:37.062 --> 00:27:39.455
un zi iz geven eyn baleboste in der velt!

00:27:39.579 --> 00:27:43.837
zire geesn iz gevezn az ikh ken mir nisht UNK dem esn.

00:27:43.781 --> 00:27:45.491
mir vel redn mer

00:27:45.491 --> 00:27:46.588
eyn minut,

00:27:46.588 --> 00:27:48.883
vart eyn minut.

00:27:48.928 --> 00:27:50.239
eyn minut yetst.
